objects.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> KeyId => Str

Specifies the ID of the Amazon Web Services Key Management Service
(Amazon Web Services KMS) symmetric encryption customer managed key to
use for encrypting generated manifest objects.



